Class FtpCmdRnfr

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.apporiented.hermesftp.cmd.AbstractFtpCmd
      • de.apporiented.hermesftp.cmd.impl.FtpCmdRnfr
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FtpCmd, FtpConstants, Cloneable

    public class FtpCmdRnfr
extends AbstractFtpCmd
    RENAME FROM (RNFR)

    This command specifies the old pathname of the file which is to be renamed. This command must be immediately followed by a "rename to" command specifying the new file pathname.

    [Excerpt from RFC-959, Postel and Reynolds]

    Author:
    Lars Behnke
